What is shell?
Shell is nothing but a interpreter between user and kernel

What is scripting?
Scripting is set of ocmmands to perform a task

What is shell scripting
It is a file with set of commands to perform from top to bottom to complete a task 
File name is always ends with .sh (optional but better if we use)
It is run using 
   ==> sh script.sh
   ==> ./script.sh
        ==> chmod +x script.sh
   ==> bash script.sh
